Optimal Unwind: Weekly vs Monthly

Pritam Dalal

3/9/2019

library(tidyverse)
##  Attaching packages  tidyverse 1.2.1 
##  ggplot2 3.1.0      purrr   0.2.5
##  tibble  1.4.2      dplyr   0.7.8
##  tidyr   0.8.2      stringr 1.3.1
##  readr   1.3.1      forcats 0.3.0
##  Conflicts  tidyverse_conflicts() 
##  dplyr::filter() masks stats::filter()
##  dplyr::lag()    masks stats::lag()
df_pnl_weekly <- 
    read_csv("data_output/weekly/gld_weekly_2014_2018_managed_pnl.csv")
## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   .default = col_double(),
##   strategy = col_character(),
##   expiration = col_date(format = ""),
##   data_date = col_date(format = ""),
##   breach = col_logical()
## )
## See spec(...) for full column specifications.
df_pnl_monthly <- 
    read_csv("data_output/monthly/gld_monthly_2014_2018_managed_pnl.csv")
## Parsed with column specification:
## cols(
##   .default = col_double(),
##   strategy = col_character(),
##   expiration = col_date(format = ""),
##   data_date = col_date(format = ""),
##   breach = col_logical()
## )
## See spec(...) for full column specifications.
df_pnl_weekly %>% 
    filter(strategy == "strangle") %>% 
    filter(variation == 0.1) %>% 
    filter(dh_threshold == 0) %>% 
    group_by(loss_trigger, data_date) %>% 
    summarize(
        dh_pnl = sum(scaled_managed_pnl)
    ) %>% 
    group_by(loss_trigger) %>% 
    summarize(
        avg_pnl = mean(dh_pnl)
        , sd_pnl = sd(dh_pnl)
        , sharpe = (mean(dh_pnl) / sd(dh_pnl)) * sqrt(252)
    ) %>% 
    ggplot() + 
        geom_point(aes(x=loss_trigger, y=sharpe)) +
        labs(
            title = "weekly: delta-hedge"
        )

df_pnl_monthly %>% 
    filter(strategy == "strangle") %>% 
    filter(variation == 0.1) %>% 
    filter(dh_threshold == 0) %>% 
    group_by(loss_trigger, data_date) %>% 
    summarize(
        dh_pnl = sum(scaled_managed_pnl)
    ) %>% 
    group_by(loss_trigger) %>% 
    summarize(
        avg_pnl = mean(dh_pnl)
        , sd_pnl = sd(dh_pnl)
        , sharpe = (mean(dh_pnl) / sd(dh_pnl)) * sqrt(252)
    ) %>% 
    ggplot() + 
        geom_point(aes(x=loss_trigger, y=sharpe)) +
        labs(
            title = "monthly: delta-hedge"
        )

df_pnl_weekly %>% 
    filter(strategy == "strangle") %>% 
    filter(variation == 0.1) %>% 
    filter(dh_threshold == 1) %>% 
    group_by(loss_trigger, data_date) %>% 
    summarize(
        dh_pnl = sum(scaled_managed_pnl)
    ) %>% 
    group_by(loss_trigger) %>% 
    summarize(
        avg_pnl = mean(dh_pnl)
        , sd_pnl = sd(dh_pnl)
        , sharpe = (mean(dh_pnl) / sd(dh_pnl)) * sqrt(252)
    ) %>% 
    ggplot() + 
        geom_point(aes(x=loss_trigger, y=sharpe)) + 
        labs(
            title = "weekly: naked"
        )

df_pnl_monthly %>% 
    filter(strategy == "strangle") %>% 
    filter(variation == 0.1) %>% 
    filter(dh_threshold == 1) %>% 
    group_by(loss_trigger, data_date) %>% 
    summarize(
        dh_pnl = sum(scaled_managed_pnl)
    ) %>% 
    group_by(loss_trigger) %>% 
    summarize(
        avg_pnl = mean(dh_pnl)
        , sd_pnl = sd(dh_pnl)
        , sharpe = (mean(dh_pnl) / sd(dh_pnl)) * sqrt(252)
    ) %>% 
    ggplot() + 
        geom_point(aes(x = loss_trigger, y = sharpe)) +
        labs(
            title = "monthly: naked"
        )
